On Escalation Ticket # 00413048 the new comment has been added: Andrei Pop:

The customer has an update regarding this.

"At first it was again not possible to write to the drives.

Then we uninstalled EPP, but it was still not possible to write to the drive (this time we did not try to remove the device driver). Instead, my colleague immediately came up with the idea of uninstalling Samsung Magician, after which it was possible to write to the drives. We then reinstalled EPP and it was still possible to write to the drives."
